(42, 8, 13, 26, 33, 32, 32, 'receive the word with joy', 'Response to God''s Word', 'This connection highlights the theme of receiving God''s word with joy but failing to act on it. Both passages emphasize the superficial reception of the message, leading to a lack of true commitment or action.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 13, 61, 2, 22, 22, 'fall away', 'Falling Away and Returning', 'This connection highlights the theme of falling away from faith. Both passages emphasize the idea of individuals who initially receive the word with joy but ultimately revert to their previous state, illustrating a lack of true commitment.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 13, 65, 1, 12, 12, NULL, 'Connection of Spiritual Fruitlessness', 'Both passages emphasize the lack of spiritual depth and fruitfulness. Luke describes those who believe temporarily without roots, while Jude refers to trees without fruit, indicating a similar theme of spiritual barrenness.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
