(42, 8, 15, 62, 2, 3, 3, 'keep it', 'Connection of Obedience and Fruitfulness', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of keeping commandments or the word. In Luke, those with a good heart bring forth fruit, while in 1 John, knowing Him is linked to keeping His commandments.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
